title: Restaurant Turistico Dona Clorina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Peruvian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has vegetarian options, including Peruvian vegetable fried rice and traditional Andes dishes such as squash and vegetables with steamed rice or lima beans and vegetables with steamed rice. Whole section of the menu is lacto-ovo vegetarian.
